        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Accurate Data for Defense (ADD) Resiliency Act</strong></p> <p>This bill requires the Department of Defense to develop and implement a process to ensure it uses analytical tools that are accurate and effective in projecting the costs and performance of energy resilience measures on military installations.<br> </p>]]>
        </text>
